spell_tooltip.description: Heals the friendly target for 12,474, then jumps up to 15 yards to heal the 3 most injured nearby allies. Healing is reduced by 30% with each jump.
Hurls molten lava at the target, dealing 5,245 Fire damage. Lava Burst will always critically strike if the target is affected by Flame Shock.
Shift partially into the elemental planes, taking 40% less damage for 12 sec.
Hurls a lightning bolt at the enemy, dealing 3,502 Nature damage and then jumping to additional nearby enemies. Affects 3 total targets.
Disrupts the target's concentration with a burst of wind, interrupting spellcasting and preventing any spell in that school from being cast for 2 sec.
Reduces the cooldown of Astral Shift by 30 sec.
Astral Shift reduces damage taken by an additional 20%.
While transformed into a Ghost Wolf, you gain 5% increased movement speed and 5% damage reduction every 1 sec, stacking up to 4 times.
Ghost Wolf removes snares and increases your movement speed by an additional 25% for the first 3 sec. May only occur once every 20 sec.
Chills the target with frost, causing 3,453 Frost damage and reducing the target's movement speed by 50% for 6 sec.

When you deal damage with a melee weapon, you have a chance to gain Maelstrom Weapon, stacking up to 5 times. Each stack of Maelstrom Weapon reduces the cast time of your next damage or healing spell by 20%.

A maximum of 5 stacks of Maelstrom Weapon can be consumed at a time.

Protects the target with an earthen shield, increasing your healing on them by 20% and healing them for 3,930 when they take damage. This heal can only occur once every few seconds. Maximum 9 charges.

Earth Shield can only be placed on one target at a time. Only one Elemental Shield can be active on the Shaman.
Increases all Fire and Frost damage you deal by 3%.

Calls forth a Greater Earth Elemental to protect you and your allies for 1 min.

While this elemental is active, your maximum health is increased by 15%.
Summons a totem at the target location that gathers electrical energy from the surrounding air and explodes after 2 sec, stunning all enemies within 8 yards for 3 sec.
Cleanse Spirit, Wind Shear, Purge, and totem casts no longer cancel Ghost Wolf.
Maximum health increased by 8%, and while you are at full health, Reincarnation cools down 75% faster.

Increases the number of Elemental Shields you can have active on yourself by 1.

You can have Earth Shield on yourself and one ally at the same time.

Summons a totem at your feet for 15 sec that heals an injured party or raid member within 40 yards for 2,581 every 1.8 sec.

If you already know Healing Stream Totem, instead gain 1 additional charge of Healing Stream Totem.
Increases Leech by 2% and reduces damage taken from area-of-effect attacks by 2%.
Summons a totem at your feet that shakes the ground around it for 10 sec, removing Fear, Charm and Sleep effects from party and raid members within 30 yards.
Reduces the cooldown of Capacitor Totem by 5 sec for each enemy it stuns, up to a maximum reduction of 20 sec.
When Capacitor Totem fades or is destroyed, another Capacitor Totem is automatically dropped in the same place.
Purges the enemy target, removing 1 beneficial Magic effect.
Purges the enemy target, removing 2 beneficial Magic effects.
Increases your attack speed by 15% for your next 3 melee swings after dealing a critical strike with a spell or ability.
Increases the healing done by Healing Stream Totem by 40%.
Increases the healing done by Healing Stream Totem by 80%.
Removes all Curse effects from a friendly target.

Summons a totem at the target location for 20 sec. The totem pulses every 2 sec, rooting all enemies within 8 yards for 8 sec. Enemies previously rooted by the totem instead suffer 50% movement speed reduction.
Summons a totem at the target location for 15 sec, continually granting all allies who pass within 10 yards 40% increased movement speed for 5 sec.
Transforms the enemy into a frog for 1 min. While hexed, the victim is incapacitated, and cannot attack or cast spells. Damage may cancel the effect. Limit 1. Only works on Humanoids and Beasts.
Increases the critical strike chance of your Nature spells and abilities by 2%.
Increases the critical strike chance of your Nature spells and abilities by 4%.

Increases the damage dealt by Lightning Shield by 50%.

Increases the healing done by Earth Shield by 12%.

Increases the damage dealt by Lightning Shield by 100%.

Increases the healing done by Earth Shield by 25%.
Reduces all magic damage taken by 2%.
Reduces all magic damage taken by 4%.
When your health is brought below 35%, you instantly heal for 10% of your maximum health. Cannot occur more than once every 45 sec.
When your health is brought below 35%, you instantly heal for 20% of your maximum health. Cannot occur more than once every 45 sec.
Reduces the cooldown of Hex by 15 sec.
Your Hex target is slowed by 70% during Hex and for 6 sec after it ends.

Increases the movement speed bonus of Ghost Wolf by 5%.

When you have 3 or more totems active, your movement speed is increased by 8%.

Increases the movement speed bonus of Ghost Wolf by 10%.

When you have 3 or more totems active, your movement speed is increased by 15%.
Calls upon the guidance of the spirits for 15 sec, permitting movement while casting Shaman spells. Castable while casting.
Calls down a bolt of lightning, dealing 575 Nature damage to all enemies within 10 yards, reducing their movement speed by 40% for 5 sec, and knocking them away from the Shaman. Usable while stunned.

Increases the radius of your totem effects by 8%.

Increases the duration of your Earthbind and Earthgrab Totems by 5 sec.

Increases the duration of your Healing Stream, Tremor, Poison Cleansing, and Wind Rush Totems by 1.5 sec.

Increases the radius of your totem effects by 15%.

Increases the duration of your Earthbind and Earthgrab Totems by 10 sec.

Increases the duration of your Healing Stream, Tremor, Poison Cleansing, and Wind Rush Totems by 3.0 sec.
Removes all movement impairing effects and increases your movement speed by 60% for 8 sec.
A gust of wind hurls you forward.
Reduces the cooldown of Spiritwalker's Grace by 30 sec and increases your movement speed by 20% while it is active.
When you cast Spiritwalker's Grace, you become immune to Silence and Interrupt effects for 5 sec.
For the next 10 sec, 25% of your healing done and 25% of your damage done is converted to healing on up to 3 nearby injured party or raid members, up to 40,780 healing to each target per second.
Relocates your active totems to the specified location.
Reduces the cooldown of your totems by 3 sec.
Reduces the cooldown of your totems by 6 sec.

Reduces the cooldown of Spirit Walk by 10 sec.

Reduces the cooldown of Gust of Wind by 5 sec.

Reduces the cooldown of Spirit Walk by 20 sec.

Reduces the cooldown of Gust of Wind by 10 sec.

Your Lava Burst casts restore 350 mana to you and 4 allies nearest to you within 40 yards.

Allies can only benefit from one Shaman's Mana Spring effect at a time, prioritizing healers.
Thunderstorm knocks enemies up instead of away and its cooldown is reduced by 5 sec.
Grips the target in lightning, stunning and dealing 38,577 Nature damage over 5 sec while the target is lassoed. Can move while channeling.
Summons a totem at your feet that removes all Poison effects from a nearby party or raid member within 30 yards every 1.5 sec for 6 sec.
Resets the cooldown of your most recently used totem with a base cooldown shorter than 3 minutes.
Your next healing or damaging Nature spell is instant cast and costs no mana.
Summons a totem at your feet for 15 sec that grants 10% physical damage reduction to you and the 4 allies nearest to the totem within 30 yards.
Summons a totem at your feet for 20 sec that prevents cast pushback and reduces the duration of all incoming interrupt effects by 50% for you and the 4 allies nearest to the totem within 30 yards.
Reduces the cooldown of Totemic Recall by 60 sec.
Totemic Recall affects an additional totem.
Instantly shocks the target with concussive force, causing 15,513 Nature damage.

Causes the earth within 8 yards of the target location to tremble and break, dealing 7,536 Physical damage over 6 sec and has a 5% chance to knock the enemy down. Multiple uses of Earthquake may overlap.
Your damaging critical strikes deal 250% damage instead of the usual 200%.

Calls forth a Greater Fire Elemental to rain destruction on your enemies for 30 sec. 

While the Fire Elemental is active, Flame Shock deals damage 
33% faster, and newly applied Flame Shocks last 100% longer.

Calls forth a Greater Storm Elemental to hurl gusts of wind that damage the Shaman's enemies for 30 sec.

While the Storm Elemental is active, each time you cast Lightning Bolt or Chain Lightning, the cast time of Lightning Bolt and Chain Lightning is reduced by 3%, stacking up to 10 times.
Increases the chance for Earthquake to knock enemies down by 3.0%.
Your successful Purge, Cleanse Spirit, Healing Stream Totem, Hex, and Wind Shear casts generate 8 Maelstrom during combat.
Your healing critical strikes heal for 250% healing instead of the usual 200%.
Casting Flame Shock reduces the mana cost of your next heal by 20% and increases its healing effectiveness by 30%.
Your Healing Surge is 25% more effective on yourself.
While you have an elemental active, your damage taken is reduced by 5%.
Increases the damage of your Lightning Bolt, Chain Lightning, and Storm Elemental by 15%.
Increases the Maelstrom generated by Lightning Bolt and Lava Burst by 2, and their Elemental Overloads by 1.
Your Flame Shock damage over time has a 10% chance to reset the remaining cooldown on Lava Burst and cause your next Lava Burst to be instant.

Reduces the cast time of Lightning Bolt and Chain Lightning by 0.25 sec.

Increases the duration of Earthquake by 1 sec.

Hurls frigid ice at the target, dealing 9,156 Frost damage and causing your next 4 Frost Shocks to deal 225% increased damage and generate 14 Maelstrom.

Generates 25 Maelstrom.
Increases your maximum Maelstrom by 50.
Lava Burst has an additional charge.
Increases the damage of your Flame Shock, Lava Burst, Lava Beam, and Fire Elemental by 10%.

Charge yourself with lightning, causing your next 2 Lightning Bolts to deal 150% more damage, and also causes your next 2 Lightning Bolts or Chain Lightnings to be instant cast and trigger an Elemental Overload on every target.
Casting Frost Shock increases the damage of your next Lava Burst by 20%.
Icefury causes your Frost Shocks to damage up to 3 additional enemies and targets hit take 15% increased Nature damage from your spells for 9 sec.
Earth Shock, Elemental Blast, and Earthquake have a 25% chance to refund all Maelstrom spent.

Earth Shock, Elemental Blast, and Earthquake enhance your next spell cast within 15 sec:

Flame Shock: The next cast also applies Flame Shock to 1 additional target within 8 yards of the target.

Lightning Bolt: Your next cast will cause 2 additional Elemental Overloads.

Chain Lightning: Your next cast will chain to 1 additional target.

Lava Burst: Reduces the cooldown of your Fire and Storm Elemental by 6.0 sec.

Frost Shock: Freezes the target in place for 6 sec.
Reduces the cooldown of Flame Shock by 1.5 sec and Flame Shock deals damage 15% faster.
Casting Lightning Bolt or Chain Lightning reduces the cooldown of your Nature spells by 1.0 sec.

Reduces the Maelstrom cost of Earth Shock and Earthquake by 5.

Reduces the Maelstrom cost of Elemental Blast by 7.

Reduces the Maelstrom cost of Earth Shock and Earthquake by 10.

Reduces the Maelstrom cost of Elemental Blast by 15.
Casting Lava Burst has a 13% chance to cause your next 2 Lightning Bolt or Chain Lightning casts to trigger Elemental Overload an additional time.
Casting Lava Burst has a 25% chance to cause your next 2 Lightning Bolt or Chain Lightning casts to trigger Elemental Overload an additional time.
Casting Lava Burst increases the damage or healing of your next Nature, Physical, or Frost spell by 10%.
Casting Lava Burst increases the damage or healing of your next Nature, Physical, or Frost spell by 20%.
Imbuing your weapon with Flametongue increases your Fire spell damage by 5% for 1 hour.
Harnesses the raw power of the elements, dealing 9,587 Elemental damage and increasing your Critical Strike or Haste by 3% or Mastery by 6% for 10 sec.

Blast your target with a Primordial Wave, dealing 3,570 Shadow damage and apply Flame Shock to an enemy, or heal an ally for 3,567.

Your next Healing Wave will also hit all targets affected by your Riptide for 150% of normal damage.

Casting Stormstrike has a 7% chance to activate Ascendance for 6.0 sec.

 Ascendance

Transform into an Air Ascendant for 15 sec, immediately dealing 973 Nature damage to any enemy within 8 yds, reducing the cooldown and cost of Stormstrike by 60%, and transforming your auto attack and Stormstrike into Wind attacks which bypass armor and have a 30 yd range.

Transform into a Flame Ascendant for 15 sec, replacing Chain Lightning with Lava Beam, removing the cooldown on Lava Burst, and increasing the damage of Lava Burst by an amount equal to your critical strike chance.

When you transform into the Flame Ascendant, instantly cast a Lava Burst at all enemies affected by your Flame Shock, and refresh your Flame Shock durations to 18 sec.
Your Earth, Fire, and Storm Elementals are drawn from primal elementals 80% more powerful than regular elementals, with additional abilities, and you gain direct control over them.

Summons a totem at the target location that erupts dealing 5,407 Fire damage and applying Flame Shock to 3 enemies within 8 yards. Continues hurling liquid magma at a random nearby target every 0.9 sec for 6 sec, dealing 3,192 Fire damage to all enemies within 8 yards.

After casting Earth Shock, your next Earthquake deals 60% additional damage.

After casting Elemental Blast, your next Earthquake deals 70% additional damage.

After casting Earth Shock, your next Earthquake deals 120% additional damage.

After casting Elemental Blast, your next Earthquake deals 140% additional damage.
Dealing direct Fire, Frost, and Nature damage within 10 sec will increase all damage dealt by 8% for 10 sec. This can only occur once every 30 sec.
Dealing direct Fire, Frost, and Nature damage within 10 sec will increase all damage dealt by 15% for 10 sec. This can only occur once every 30 sec.
Lava Burst and Lava Burst Overload damage reduces the cooldown of Primordial Wave by 0.5 sec.
Lava Burst and Lava Burst Overload damage reduces the cooldown of Primordial Wave by 1.0 sec.
Increases the damage dealt by your Elemental Overloads by 8%.
Increases the damage dealt by your Elemental Overloads by 15%.
Reduces the cooldown of Ascendance by 30 sec, and you gain 8% additional Haste while Ascendance is active.
Reduces the cooldown of Ascendance by 60 sec, and you gain 15% additional Haste while Ascendance is active.
Flame Shock damage increases the damage of your next Earth Shock, Elemental Blast, or Earthquake by 1.5%, stacking up to 20 times.
Flame Shock damage increases the damage of your next Earth Shock, Elemental Blast, or Earthquake by 3.0%, stacking up to 20 times.
Flame Shock damage has a 100% chance to generate 1 Maelstrom.
Flame Shock damage has a 100% chance to generate 2 Maelstrom.
Earth Shock, Elemental Blast, and Earthquake make your target a Lightning Rod for 8 sec. Lightning Rods take 20% of all damage you deal with Lightning Bolt and Chain Lightning.

Charge yourself with lightning, causing your next 2 Lightning Bolts to deal 150% more damage, and also causes your next 2 Lightning Bolts or Chain Lightnings to be instant cast and trigger an Elemental Overload on every target.
Casting Primordial Wave triggers Lava Surge immediately and every 3 sec for 12 sec. Lava Surges triggered by Primordial Wave increase the damage of your next Lava Burst by 15%.
Each additional Lightning Bolt generated by Primordial Wave increases your Haste by 10% for 12 sec.

Earth Shock, Elemental Blast, and Earthquake can trigger your Mastery: Elemental Overload at 50% effectiveness.

Overloaded Earthquakes do not knock enemies down.

Casting Earth Shock or Earthquake while Ascendance is active extends the duration of Ascendance by 2.5 sec.

Casting Elemental Blast while Ascendance is active extends the duration of Ascendance by 3.5 sec.
When you cast Earth Shock, Elemental Blast, or Earthquake, gain Lava Surge and increase the damage of your next Lava Burst by 10%.
Flame Shock damage over time critical strikes reduce the cooldown of your Fire and Storm Elemental by 1.0 sec, and Flame Shock has a 50% increased critical strike chance.
